data.description: This 2-story home includes a finished walk out LL providing you with three levels of open living space. This updated home features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. The total living space encompasses over 3100 finished square feet. The primary bedroom is spacious and includes a large private bathroom. Situated on just under an acre of land, there's ample room to enjoy the outdoors. The home is located on a private cul-de-sac and includes a huge primary suite with a walkout to a private deck offering silence and solitude. Additionally, there's another larger deck off the dining area that leads to the backyard with a partially fenced in area giving you ease of mind when it comes to children and pets. Inside, a gas-burning fireplace adds warmth and ambiance, while the property boasts an abundance of natural lighting and an open floor plan. This property is located in Ham Lake, Minnesota, overlooking beautiful Lake Netta with 65 feet of lake frontage offering a tranquil and convenient location.
